  "text": "tional). The grids were washed, postfixed with 2% glutaraldehyde, rinsed with ddH2O, and dried. The sections were stained with 2% uranyl acetate for 15 min and 3% lead citrate for 1 min and observed with a Hitachi H-7100 transmission electron microscope [CITATION_1] . Statistical analysis. Results were expressed as means Ϯ SE. For comparisons between two groups, the paired or unpaired Student's t test (two tailed) was used. For multiple comparisons, the one-way ANOVA was used. KaplanMeier method was used to calculate the survival data. A P value Ͻ0.05 was considered significant when determined by the Mann-Whitney U test.",
